    "Name": "Hammerhead",
    "Details": "An early experimental prototype of the Hammerhead. Instead of the hardened armor of the production model, a combination of Spall Liner, Modular Armor and Reinforced Legs were used. Carrying two medium pulse lasers, one ER medium laser and two SRM-6 launchers, meant the 'Mech could only engage at quite close ranges which proved to be a major flaw and lead to the changes of the production model.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Battle Fists</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.04</color></b>",
